      "explanation": "$\\alpha^3 + \\beta^3 = S^3 - 3PS = -27/8 + 45/4 = 63/8 = 7.875$.",
      "steps": [
        {
          "text": "**Vieta:** $S = -b/a = -3/2$, $P = c/a = 5/2$."
        },
        {
          "text": "**Identity:**"
        },
        {
          "math": "\\alpha^3 + \\beta^3 = (\\alpha + \\beta)^3 - 3\\alpha\\beta(\\alpha + \\beta) = S^3 - 3PS"
        },
        {
          "math": "= \\left(-\\dfrac{3}{2}\\right)^3 - 3\\left(\\dfrac{5}{2}\\right)\\left(-\\dfrac{3}{2}\\right)"
        },
        {
          "math": "= -\\dfrac{27}{8} + \\dfrac{45}{4} = -\\dfrac{27}{8} + \\dfrac{90}{8} = \\dfrac{63}{8} = 7.875"
        }
      ],
      "difficulty": "hard"
    },
